extendedInfo.description: Our Pyongyang Mobile Application gives you full access to Pyongyang in North KoreaThe Application gives you general infos, a photo library, Hotels in Pyongyang, Google Satellite Maps for Pyongyang and as well North Korea.We also included a Pyongyang Travel Guide and a navigational compass.This application is compatible from Android Froyo, Gingerbread, Honeycomb, Ice Cream Sandwich, and the latest Jelly Bean.
